## Current Role (2025-2026)

Sahar Abdelnabi is a Principal Investigator at the ELLIS Institute Tübingen and leads the COMPASS research group (COoperative Machine intelligence for People-Aligned Safe Systems). She was previously an AI Security researcher at Microsoft and completed her PhD at CISPA Helmholtz Center for Information Security.

