- With the Incalmo toolkit, models successfully replicated attacks similar to known breaches, though autonomous capabilities remain limited

**Biosecurity Red-Teaming:**
- Models exceeded "world-class virology expert baselines" on troubleshooting evaluations
- Internal testing showed models approaching expert performance on protocols and DNA manipulation
